


User Commands                                         SUMATTN7(1)



NAME
     sumattn7 - add or subtract ECAT7 attenuation files


SYNOPSIS
     sumattn7 file1,f1 file2,f2 outfile

     where: out = (f1 * file1) + (f2 * file2)


DESCRIPTION
     This program adds a pair of  ECAT7  attenuation  files  with
     scaling factors applied. Using negative factors permits sub-
     traction; 0.5 for both scaling factors creates  an  averaged
     attenuation.


EXAMPLE
     sumattn7 p5000tr1.a,.5 p5000tr2.a,.5 p5000tr3.a


RELATED PROGRAMS
     fpattn7, sino


